---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="바위로드 서비스 소개 | 수수료 0원 필리핀 어학연수"
  description="수수료 0원, 출국 전부터 현지 생활까지. 바위로드만의 필리핀 어학연수 동행 서비스를 소개합니다."
  path="/with-bawi"
>
  <div class="bg-cream">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="pt-[140px] pb-16 px-6 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-green-badge text-accent-green-dark px-3 py-1.5 rounded-2xl text-[0.75rem] font-semibold mb-5 animate-fade-in-up">
          바위로드 서포트
        </div>
        <h1
          class="text-[2rem] md:text-[3rem] font-black leading-[1.25] tracking-tight text-brown-dark animate-fade-in-up"
          style="animation-delay: 0.1s"
        >
          바위로드가 함께하는
          <br />
          <span class="text-terracotta">특별한 출국 준비</span>
        </h1>
        <p
          class="mt-5 text-[0.95rem] md:text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.7] text-brown animate-fade-in-up"
          style="animation-delay: 0.2s"
        >
          단순한 유학원 소개가 아닌, 출국 전부터 현지 도착까지
          <br />
          바위로드만의 케어 서비스를 경험하세요.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STEP 01: 출국 전 1:1 오리엔테이션 -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-terracotta-light text-terracotta px-3 py-1.5 rounded-2xl text-[0.75rem] font-semibold mb-4">
            STEP 01
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-[1.6rem] md:text-[2.2rem] font-extrabold tracking-tight text-brown-dark leading-[1.3]">
            출국 전 1:1 오리엔테이션
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-5 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] text-brown">
            출국 전 담당 매니저와 <strong>1:1로 진행하는 맞춤형 오리엔테이션</strong>입니다. 어학원 생활부터
            현지 적응까지 꼭 알아야 할 정보를 미리 파악하고, <strong>첫날부터 자신 있게 시작</strong>할 수
            있도록 준비해드립니다.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              현지 생활 필수 정보 안내 (교통, 환전, 유심 등)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              어학원 첫날 가이드 &amp; 수업 준비
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              준비물 체크리스트 제공
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              현지 긴급 연락망 안내
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal rounded-[20px] aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521737604893-d14cc237f11d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
            alt="1:1 오리엔테이션 상담"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STEP 02: 바위로드 웰컴 키트 증정 -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
        <div class="reveal text-center mb-14">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-terracotta-light text-terracotta px-3 py-1.5 rounded-2xl text-[0.75rem] font-semibold mb-4">
            STEP 02
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-[1.6rem] md:text-[2.2rem] font-extrabold tracking-tight text-brown-dark leading-[1.3]">
            바위로드 웰컴 키트 증정
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.7] text-brown max-w-[600px] mx-auto">
            출국하는 모든 학생에게 바위로드가 직접 준비한 웰컴 키트를 드립니다.
            <br />
            낯선 땅에서의 첫 발걸음을 함께 응원합니다.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
          <!-- 여행용 멀티어댑터 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[16px] border border-beige-dark p-6 flex flex-col items-start gap-4 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-terracotta-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-terracotta"><path d="M12 22v-5"/><path d="M9 8V2"/><path d="M15 8V2"/><path d="M18 8v5a4 4 0 0 1-4 4h-4a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[0.95rem] font-bold text-brown-dark mb-2">여행용 멀티어댑터</h3>
              <p class="text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.6] text-brown">필리핀 콘센트 규격에 맞는 멀티어댑터로 도착 즉시 편리하게 사용하세요.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 바위로드 트래블 파우치 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[16px] border border-beige-dark p-6 flex flex-col items-start gap-4 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-terracotta-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-terracotta"><path d="M16 20V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="6" rx="2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[0.95rem] font-bold text-brown-dark mb-2">바위로드 트래블 파우치</h3>
              <p class="text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.6] text-brown">여행 필수품을 깔끔하게 정리할 수 있는 바위로드 전용 파우치입니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 필리핀 생활 가이드북 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[16px] border border-beige-dark p-6 flex flex-col items-start gap-4 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-terracotta-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-terracotta"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[0.95rem] font-bold text-brown-dark mb-2">필리핀 생활 가이드북</h3>
              <p class="text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.6] text-brown">현지 생활에 꼭 필요한 정보를 담은 바위로드 맞춤형 가이드북입니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 응원 손편지 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[16px] border border-beige-dark p-6 flex flex-col items-start gap-4 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-terracotta-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-terracotta"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[0.95rem] font-bold text-brown-dark mb-2">응원 손편지</h3>
              <p class="text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.6] text-brown">바위로드 팀이 직접 쓴 응원 편지로 새로운 시작을 함께 응원합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STEP 03: 현지 공항 픽업 서비스 -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="reveal rounded-[20px] aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden order-last md:order-first">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1436491865332-7a61a109cc05?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
            alt="공항 픽업 서비스"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-terracotta-light text-terracotta px-3 py-1.5 rounded-2xl text-[0.75rem] font-semibold mb-4">
            STEP 03
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-[1.6rem] md:text-[2.2rem] font-extrabold tracking-tight text-brown-dark leading-[1.3]">
            현지 공항 픽업 서비스
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-5 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] text-brown">
            처음 방문하는 낯선 나라에서 혼자 이동하는 걱정은 접어두세요. 필리핀 도착과 동시에
            <strong>바위로드 현지 스태프가 직접 공항으로 마중</strong>을 나갑니다. 어학원까지 안전하게
            이동하고, 첫날 정착까지 함께합니다.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              마닐라/세부/클락 주요 공항 픽업
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              어학원까지 안전한 차량 이동
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              현지 스태프 동행 안내
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              첫날 정착 서포트
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BOTTOM CTA -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-brown-dark text-center relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute -top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[700px] h-[700px] bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(196,96,58,0.18)_0%,transparent_70%)] rounded-full"></div>
      <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto relative">
        <h2 class="text-[1.8rem] md:text-[2.6rem] font-black leading-[1.25] tracking-tight text-cream">
          바위로드와 함께
          <br />
          <span class="text-terracotta-light">걱정 없는 어학연수</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[0.95rem] md:text-[1.05rem] leading-[1.7] text-brown-light">
          출국 준비부터 현지 도착까지, 모든 과정을 함께합니다.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex gap-3.5 justify-center flex-wrap">
          <a
            href="/inquiry?from=with-bawi"
            class="bg-terracotta text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-[10px] text-base font-bold no-underline inline-flex items-center gap-2 shadow-[0_4px_14px_rgba(196,96,58,0.4)] hover:bg-terracotta-hover hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all"
          >
            무료 상담 신청
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/quote?from=with-bawi"
            class="bg-transparent text-cream px-8 py-3.5 rounded-[10px] text-base font-semibold border-2 border-white/30 no-underline inline-flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/50 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all"
          >
            견적서 받기
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
    (entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          (entry.target as HTMLElement).style.opacity = "1";
          (entry.target as HTMLElement).style.transform = "translateY(0)";
        }
      });
    },
    { threshold: 0.1 },
  );
  document.querySelectorAll(".reveal").forEach((el) => {
    const htmlEl = el as HTMLElement;
    htmlEl.style.opacity = "0";
    htmlEl.style.transform = "translateY(20px)";
    htmlEl.style.transition = "all 0.5s ease";
    observer.observe(el);
  });
</script>
